            <entry xml:id="entry_agarc" xml:lang="os">
                <form xml:lang="os-x-iron" type="lemma"><orth>agarc</orth></form>
                <form xml:lang="os-x-digor" type="dialectal"><orth>agarcæ</orth></form>
                <sense><def xml:lang="ru">какая-то мера длины</def><def xml:lang="en">a kind of unit
                        of length</def><note type="comment" xml:lang="ru">(в выражении <mentioned
                            xml:lang="os"><lang/>
                            <w>avd agarcy</w>
                            <gloss><q>семь %sagarc%sʼов</q></gloss></mentioned>) </note><note
                        type="comment" xml:lang="en">(in the expression <mentioned xml:lang="os"><lang/>
                            <w>avd agarcy</w>
                            <gloss><q>seven %sagarc%s's</q></gloss></mentioned>) </note></sense>
                <abv:exampleGrp>
                    <abv:example xml:lang="os-x-digor">
                        <usg><lang/></usg>
                        <quote>avd agarci ka xezuj wæxæn topp</quote>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="ru">
                            <q>ружье, пробивающее семь %sagarc%sʼов</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <abv:tr xml:lang="en">
                            <q>a gun that hits seven %sagarc%sʼ</q>
                        </abv:tr>
                        <bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_СОПам."/><biblScope>II
                            126</biblScope></bibl>
                    </abv:example>
                </abv:exampleGrp>
                <etym xml:lang="ru">Вероятно, из <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ag"/> ‘котел’ и <ref
                        type="xr" target="#entry_arc"/> ’копье’: длина жерди („копья”), на которую
                    подвешивался котел?</etym>
                <etym xml:lang="en">Probably from <ref type="xr" target="#entry_ag"/> ‘kettle’ and
                        <ref type="xr" target="#entry_arc"/> ’spear’: length of the pole (“spear”)
                    on which the kettle was hung?</etym>
            </entry>
